<div class='post-body entry-content' id='post-body-7043737823965390635' itemprop='description articleBody'>
<p>&nbsp;<b><span style="font-family: Times New Roman, serif; font-size: medium;"><span style="font-size: x-large;">a call of CPI(Maoist)</span></span></b></p><p><span style="font-size: large;"><b><span style="font-family: Times New Roman, serif;">Let
 us hail the revolutionary contributions of Comrade Jose Maria Sison and
 Commemorate his Memorial Day on 16th Jan, 2023 across the World</span></b></span></p><p><b><span style="font-family: Times New Roman, serif; font-size: medium;">_---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------MaoistRoad
 and ICSPWI&nbsp; support this call and Invite all Parties and Organisations 
mlm, revolutionaries for all form of initiatives as First Tribute to 
Comrade Ka Joma and for supporting People's War in Philippinesplease inform about this - maoistroad@gmail.com or csgpindia@gmail.com</span></b></p><p><b><span style="font-family: Times New Roman, serif; font-size: medium;">International Poster&nbsp; <br /></span></b></p><p><b><span style="font-family: Times New Roman, serif; font-size: medium;">&nbsp;<br /></span></b></p><p><b><span style="font-family: Times New Roman, serif; font-size: medium;"></span></b></p><div class="separator" style="clear: both; text-align: center;"><b><span style="font-family: Times New Roman, serif; font-size: medium;"><a href="https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEik9c98EulA1sRSo9chDvIbuBQ8fnBMNChiSf_xhVJL5o-Zh9ZzYGqO499QJU3S6cw9AVgO4TSwHT3mu4fpOkTvJwp7WmIpaeTS4FhQNKC9D2XIcHjSqEMor5Sl3QrLCLWmnVuiO2fYxIwdu0-bQCuAxOyVO8HS2S5TX3dshkn609BlRh2Viq0ApVf3/s2478/joma-memorial-v2_eng_web.png" style="margin-left: 1em; margin-right: 1em;"><img border="0" data-original-height="2478" data-original-width="1752" height="640" src="https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEik9c98EulA1sRSo9chDvIbuBQ8fnBMNChiSf_xhVJL5o-Zh9ZzYGqO499QJU3S6cw9AVgO4TSwHT3mu4fpOkTvJwp7WmIpaeTS4FhQNKC9D2XIcHjSqEMor5Sl3QrLCLWmnVuiO2fYxIwdu0-bQCuAxOyVO8HS2S5TX3dshkn609BlRh2Viq0ApVf3/w452-h640/joma-memorial-v2_eng_web.png" width="452" /></a></span></b></div><b><span style="font-family: Times New Roman, serif; font-size: medium;"><span style="font-size: x-large;">a<div class="separator" style="clear: both; text-align: center;"><a href="https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEgom0leUm_Mv951W4kBpm7MfGyn_KpgKfSUS3mE8bHrq7mNk9NoEETA_nqPvzgQFIGuqEEipF3R_e10yU6xmjuFE4cURc-H-Ibu0o_Y6_rjQtueZgBLPjpaaBio3tNrRSy9dxUw7oh1edWtdsEh83v_2-VYea6B66fM8Dki7vUJXa5JtrNv-tpXTqsV/s2478/joma-memorial-v2_spa_web.png" imageanchor="1" style="margin-left: 1em; margin-right: 1em;"><img border="0" data-original-height="2478" data-original-width="1752" height="640" src="https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/i